<invoker type="RESTful">
    <name>otrs</name>
    <description>OTRS (originally Open-Source Ticket Request System) is a service management suite. The suite contains an agent portal, admin dashboard and customer portal. You find here the api reference https://doc.otrs.com/doc/api/otrs/8.0/Perl/</description>
